cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

This paper is about a collection of experiments designed to investigate core capabilities of reinforcement learning (RL) agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the automation of evaluation and analysis of agents, which suggests a possible fit with cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
